des:
Attempt to "Launch ze missiles" and maybe Alexa will let you, or not. This is a silly, just-for-fun skill. You can now "Launch ze Missiles" whenever you want to, or if you ever feel the need for missiles.

Someone made a bad joke? Launch ze missiles!
Work getting you down? Launch ze missiles!
No good reason? Launch ze missiles!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
